    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="第二次上机安排-第7周"><a class="header-anchor" href="#第二次上机安排-第7周">¶</a><em>第二次上机安排 (第7周)</em></h2><h3 id="1-用plot绘制曲线："><a class="header-anchor" href="#1-用plot绘制曲线：">¶</a>（1） 用plot绘制曲线：</h3><p>$y=e^{-t/3}sin2t$</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">t = linspace(0,pi,1e2);                  % 定义变量</span><br><span class="line">y = exp(t/3).*sin(2*t);                  % 相应的y向量</span><br><span class="line">plot(t,y,&apos;-r&apos;,&apos;LineWidth&apos;,2);            </span><br><span class="line">axis(0,4*pi,-1,1);</span><br><span class="line">xlabel(&apos;t&apos;);</span><br><span class="line">ylabel(&apos;y&apos;);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="2-用ezplot绘制曲线："><a class="header-anchor" href="#2-用ezplot绘制曲线：">¶</a>（2） 用ezplot绘制曲线：</h3><p>$y=2/3 e^{t/2} cos(\frac{\sqrt{3}}{2}t)$ 和它积分$s(t) = \int^{t}_0 y(t)\mathrm{d}t$</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">syms t tao</span><br><span class="line">y = 2/3 * exp(-t/2)*cos(sqrt(3)/2*t);  % def y(t)</span><br><span class="line">s = subs(int(y,t,0,tao),tao,t);        % get s(t)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">% plot</span><br><span class="line">subplot(2,1,1);</span><br><span class="line">ezplot(y,[0,4*pi]);</span><br><span class="line">ylim([-0.2,0.7]);</span><br><span class="line">grid on</span><br><span class="line">subplot(2,1,2);</span><br><span class="line">ezplot(s,[0,4*pi]);</span><br><span class="line">grid on</span><br><span class="line">title(&apos;s = \int y(t)dt&apos;);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="3-lc电路算例"><a class="header-anchor" href="#3-lc电路算例">¶</a>（3） LC电路算例</h3><p>电流源$i_x(t)$，电感L和电容C串联组成的电路。求解每个原件上的电压波形。</p><p>电流源电流：$i_x(t) = kt^2 e^{-at} sin(\omega t)$</p><p>已知参数： $k=3,a=2,\omega=1,L=0.5H, C=1F$</p><h5 id="matlab符号运算求解"><a class="header-anchor" href="#matlab符号运算求解">¶</a>matlab符号运算求解:</h5><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">clear all % clear work area of previous work.</span><br><span class="line">syms vx ix vC vxn ixn vCn vLn k a w t L C</span><br><span class="line">% current</span><br><span class="line">ix = k*t^2*exp(-a*t)*sin(w*t);</span><br><span class="line">ixn = subs(ix,[k a w],[3,2,1]);  % substitute k=3,a=2 and w=1 to ix.</span><br><span class="line">% ezplot(ixn,[0,10]);</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">% inductance voltage: vL = L*dix/dt</span><br><span class="line">vL = L*diff(ix,t);</span><br><span class="line">% vL = simple(vL);</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">% Capacitor voltage: vC = q/C</span><br><span class="line">vC = (1/C)*int(ix,t,0,t);  % integrate ix with respect to t with limits from o to t</span><br><span class="line">vx = vC + vL;  % total voltage</span><br><span class="line">vLn = subs(vL,[k a w L C],[3 2 1 0.5 1]);</span><br><span class="line">vCn = subs(vC,[k a w L C],[3 2 1 0.5 1]);</span><br><span class="line">vxn = subs(vx,[k a w L C],[3 2 1 0.5 1]);</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">% plot all the voltage in the same window</span><br><span class="line">figure;</span><br><span class="line">el = ezplot(vLn,[0,10]);</span><br><span class="line">hold on </span><br><span class="line">ec = ezplot(vCn,[0,10]);</span><br><span class="line">ex = ezplot(vxn,[0,10]);</span><br><span class="line">ylim([-0.2 0.6]);</span><br><span class="line">grid on</span><br><span class="line">set([el ec ex],&apos;linewidth&apos;,3);</span><br><span class="line">h1 = legend(&apos;V_L&apos;,&apos;V_C&apos;,&apos;V_&#123;tatal&#125;&apos;)</span><br><span class="line">set(h1,&apos;fontsize&apos;,13);</span><br><span class="line">legend(&apos;Location&apos;,&apos;best&apos;);</span><br><span class="line">legend(&apos;boxoff&apos;);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="4-rlc电路算例"><a class="header-anchor" href="#4-rlc电路算例">¶</a>(4) RLC电路算例</h3><p>电阻R，电感L和电容C分别与电流源串联组成电路。</p><p>电流源电流$i_s(t) = 0.2 exp(-1000t)$</p><p>$t=0$时刻，C，L均不储能。 其中电路参数：$C=1\mu F,R=300\Omega,L=2.5mH$</p><p>由KCL得：<br>$C\frac{du}{dt}+\frac{u}{R}+\frac{1}{L}\int^{t}_0u(t)dt = i_s(t)$</p><p>电压的一阶导数初始值：$C\frac{u(0+)}{dt}=0.2$</p><h4 id="a-matlab符号运算"><a class="header-anchor" href="#a-matlab符号运算">¶</a>a. matlab符号运算</h4><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">clear all</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">syms IL v t</span><br><span class="line">C = 1e-6; % Capacitor</span><br><span class="line">L = 2.5e-3; % Inductance</span><br><span class="line">R = 300; % Resistance</span><br><span class="line">disp([&apos;C = &apos;, num2str(C)]);</span><br><span class="line">disp([&apos;1/R = &apos;, num2str(1/R)]);</span><br><span class="line">disp([&apos;1/L = &apos;, num2str(1/L)]);</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">% D2V represents the second derivative of V.</span><br><span class="line">V = dsolve(&apos;1e-6*D2V + 0.0033*DV + 400*V = -200*exp(-1000*t)&apos;,...</span><br><span class="line">            &apos;DV(0)=0.2e6&apos;,&apos;V(0)=0&apos;);</span><br><span class="line">% Calculate the inductor current by integrating V with respect to t from</span><br><span class="line">% 0 to t and multiplying by 1/L;</span><br><span class="line">iL = 1/L *int(V,t,0,t);</span><br><span class="line">h_iL = ezplot(iL,[0 2e-3]);</span><br><span class="line">set(h_iL,&apos;linewidth&apos;,2);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="b-数值计算-采用ode"><a class="header-anchor" href="#b-数值计算-采用ode">¶</a>b. 数值计算 （采用ode）</h4><p>电路电压的二阶微分方程：<br>$C\frac{d^2 u}{d t^2}+\frac{1}{R}\frac{du}{dt}+\frac{1}{L}u(t) = \frac{d i_s(t)}{dt}$</p><p>数值计算需要降阶处理：<br>$y(1) = u; y(2)=u’$, 则设：</p><p>$dy(1)=y(2)$</p><p>$dy(2)=u’’=\frac{1}{C}[\frac{d i_s(t)}{dt}-\frac{1}{R}\frac{du}{dt}-\frac{1}{L}u] =\frac{1}{C}[\frac{d i_s(t)}{dt}-\frac{1}{R}y(2) - \frac{1}{L}y(1)]$</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">function dydt = odefcn(t,y,R,L,C)</span><br><span class="line">% filename: odefun.m</span><br><span class="line">% dydt(1) = u&apos;;</span><br><span class="line">% dydt(2) = u&quot;;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    % dis=d(is)/dt</span><br><span class="line">    function Dis = dis(t)</span><br><span class="line">         Dis = -0.2*1e3*exp(-1e3*t);  </span><br><span class="line">    end</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">dydt = zeros(2,1);</span><br><span class="line">dydt(1) = y(2);</span><br><span class="line">dydt(2) = 1/C*(dis(t)-y(2)/R-y(1)/L);</span><br><span class="line">dydt = [dydt(1); dydt(2)];</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">end</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h5 id="主程序："><a class="header-anchor" href="#主程序：">¶</a>主程序：</h5><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">% driver for ode function</span><br><span class="line">% filename: driver.m</span><br><span class="line">% firebird@TYUT</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">clear all</span><br><span class="line">close all</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">format long;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">R = 300; % Resistance</span><br><span class="line">L = 2.5e-3; % Inductance</span><br><span class="line">C = 1e-6; % Capacitor </span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">tspan = [0 1e-3];</span><br><span class="line">y0 = [0 0.2/C];</span><br><span class="line">[t,y] = ode45(@(t,y) odefcn(t,y,R,L,C), tspan, y0);</span><br><span class="line">u=y(:,1);</span><br><span class="line">% u&apos;=y(:,2);</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">% Cumulative trapezoidal numerical integration</span><br><span class="line">iL = 1/L*cumtrapz(t,u); % iL = int(u)/L</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">plot(t,iL,&apos;k&apos;,&apos;linewidth&apos;,2);</span><br><span class="line">xlabel(&apos;time[s]&apos;,&apos;fontsize&apos;,18);</span><br><span class="line">ylabel(&apos;i_L [A]&apos;,&apos;fontsize&apos;,18);</span><br><span class="line">title(&apos;i_L(t) = 1/L*\int_&#123;0&#125;^&#123;t&#125;udt&apos;,&apos;fontsize&apos;,18);</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="c-思考：-改变电阻-电感或者电容-参数观察-i-l-t"><a class="header-anchor" href="#c-思考：-改变电阻-电感或者电容-参数观察-i-l-t">¶</a>c. 思考： 改变电阻（电感或者电容），参数观察$i_L(t)$</h4><h3 id="5-rlc串联电路"><a class="header-anchor" href="#5-rlc串联电路">¶</a>（5） RLC串联电路</h3><p>稳压源电压$U_s=10$V</p><p>已知参数： $k=3,a=2,\omega=1,L=0.5H, C=1F$</p><p>由KVL得：<br>$L\frac{di}{dt} + Ri +\frac{1}{C}\int^{t}_0i(t)dt = U_s$</p><p>上述方程求导得二阶微分方程：<br>$L\frac{d^2 i}{d t^2} + R\frac{di}{dt} + \frac{1}{C}i = 0$</p><p>对于RLC电路零状态响应的初始条件： $i(0+)=0$, $\frac{di(0+)}{dt}=\frac{U_s}{L}$</p><h4 id="采用ode数值求解"><a class="header-anchor" href="#采用ode数值求解">¶</a>采用ode数值求解</h4><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br><span class="line">37</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">% RLC series circuit</span><br><span class="line">% filename: RLC_series.m</span><br><span class="line">% firebird@TYUT</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">clear all</span><br><span class="line">close all</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">format long;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">R = 300; % Resistance</span><br><span class="line">L = 2.5e-3; % Inductance</span><br><span class="line">C = 1e-6; % Capacitor </span><br><span class="line">Us = 10;  % voltage source </span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">tspan = [0 1e-3*2];</span><br><span class="line">y0 = [0 Us/L];</span><br><span class="line">[t,y] = ode45(@(t,y) odefcn(t,y,R,L,C), tspan, y0);</span><br><span class="line">icur=y(:,1); % current </span><br><span class="line">% icur&apos;=y(:,2);</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">% Cumulative trapezoidal numerical integration</span><br><span class="line">uc = 1/C*cumtrapz(t,icur); % uc = int(icur)/C</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">plot(t,uc,&apos;k&apos;,&apos;linewidth&apos;,2);</span><br><span class="line">xlabel(&apos;time[s]&apos;,&apos;fontsize&apos;,18);</span><br><span class="line">ylabel(&apos;u_c [V]&apos;,&apos;fontsize&apos;,18);</span><br><span class="line">title(&apos;u_c(t) = 1/c*\int_&#123;0&#125;^&#123;t&#125;idt&apos;,&apos;fontsize&apos;,18);</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">function dydt = odefcn(t,y,R,L,C)</span><br><span class="line">% dydt(1) = i&apos;;</span><br><span class="line">% dydt(2) = i&quot;;</span><br><span class="line">dydt = zeros(2,1);</span><br><span class="line">dydt(1) = y(2);</span><br><span class="line">dydt(2) = -1/L*(y(2)*R + y(1)/C);</span><br><span class="line">dydt = [dydt(1); dydt(2)];</span><br><span class="line">end</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="思考体"><a class="header-anchor" href="#思考体">¶</a>思考体</h4><p>如何计算RC，RL电路？</p><p><em>Hint: 采用RLC串联电路计算方法，对于 (1)RC电路：L=0;  (2)RL电路：$\frac{1}{C}\int^{t}_0i(t)dt$=0</em></p><h3 id="6-让-doc-和-help-两个命令成为用matlab的习惯"><a class="header-anchor" href="#6-让-doc-和-help-两个命令成为用matlab的习惯">¶</a>(6) 让 <em>doc</em> 和 <em>help</em> 两个命令成为用matlab的习惯！</h3><p>请同学们自己在command window输入： <em>doc cumtrapz</em> 或者 <em>help cumtrapz</em></p><p>学习<em>cumtrapz</em>如何使用。</p><h3 id="其他说明"><a class="header-anchor" href="#其他说明">¶</a>其他说明</h3><p>与Matlab功能相似，语法相近的另一个科学计算软件：Scilab，是由法国国家信息、自动化研究院的科学家们开发的“开放源码”软件。Scilab支持 Windows/Linux/mac OS，其网址：<a href="http://www.scilab.org/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">http://www.scilab.org/</a></p>]]></content>
    
